    "name": "及时抵达",
    "steam_appid": 3071060,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《及时抵达》是一款极简风格的休闲策略游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要驾驶汽车，在规定时间内吃到星星，即可过关。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特点</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >119个不同的关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >预计游戏时间：4-8小时</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持键盘鼠标和手柄控制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >循序渐进的难度</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >极简，轻松的氛围</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>简单的操作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中只有两种操作：踩下油门踏板，以及使用卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以只使用一只鼠标，就可以游玩游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/820152c308be42cd26d3767342b8d7bf.poster.avif?t=1764693750\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/820152c308be42cd26d3767342b8d7bf.webm?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/820152c308be42cd26d3767342b8d7bf.mp4?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>使用卡牌</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用卡牌，进行左转，右转或者加速。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时机也很重要，不要浪费每一张牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着游戏的进行，可以获得更多的卡牌或道具，帮助你战胜谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/3f36b3edb6e84fb977f65b73cb25cf0b.poster.avif?t=1764693750\" width=480 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/3f36b3edb6e84fb977f65b73cb25cf0b.webm?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/3f36b3edb6e84fb977f65b73cb25cf0b.mp4?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遵守规则</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不要撞车，不要撞人，遵守规则。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有不同的障碍，需要玩家进行应对。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着关卡的推进，越来越多新的机制会产生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/e8620d978ed3a908545df3b4a56b0270.poster.avif?t=1764693750\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/e8620d978ed3a908545df3b4a56b0270.webm?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/e8620d978ed3a908545df3b4a56b0270.mp4?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>小心夜路</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >据说在一些区域夜间行驶的时候，驾驶者会精神紧张——直至失去意识。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所以，尽量呆在有光的地方。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也许在商店购买一个“幽灵探测仪”会帮助你？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/600a67c8f2d35bb522ad1cdd262cd47b.poster.avif?t=1764693750\" width=480 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/600a67c8f2d35bb522ad1cdd262cd47b.webm?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/600a67c8f2d35bb522ad1cdd262cd47b.mp4?t=1764693750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
